title: Common Interview
itunes:title: Common Interview
description:
Oscar winner Common stopped by The Breakfast Club where he talked about leaving Oprah hi & dry for a high-five at The Oscars, how he felt right after his big Oscar win for 'Glory' and if he's back together with ex-girlfriend Serena Williams.
